<% content_for :title, 'Tenpai Speeder｜麻雀練習サービス' %>
<% content_for :meta_description, '登録不要で始められる麻雀練習サービス。牌効率や向聴数を可視化し、リーチ判断・終盤判断をテンポ良く鍛えられます。' %>
<% content_for :meta_keywords, '麻雀,練習,牌効率,向聴数,シミュレーター,テンパイスピーダー' %>

<% content_for :logo_link_path, root_path %>
<div class='relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-[#04060b] text-slate-100'>
  <a href='#main-content' class='sr-only absolute left-4 top-4 z-20 rounded-md bg-white/90 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow focus-visible:not-sr-only focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-cyan-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[#04060b]'>
    コンテンツへスキップ
  </a>

  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0' aria-hidden='true'>
    <div class='absolute -top-40 -left-32 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-cyan-400/15 blur-3xl'></div>
    <div class='absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-sky-500/12 blur-3xl'></div>
    <div class='absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_20%,rgba(56,189,248,0.12),transparent_35%),radial-gradient(circle_at_75%_10%,rgba(14,165,233,0.12),transparent_32%)]'></div>
  </div>

  <main id='main-content' class='relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10' tabindex='-1'>
    <header class='mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center'>
      <h1 class='mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-4xl'>
        <span class='block text-rose-500 font-serif'>Tenpai Speeder</span>
      </h1>
      <div class='mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-200/85'>
        <p>牌効率を視覚的に学べるトレーニング環境を用意しました。</p>
        <p>登録なしでもすぐにプレイでき、実戦に近いテンポで判断力を磨けます。</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class='mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr,0.8fr]'>
      <section aria-labelledby='why-title' class='rounded-3xl border border-cyan-500/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-[0_24px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.55)] backdrop-blur'>
        <h2 id='why-title' class='font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] text-cyan-200'>Why Tenpai Speeder</h2>
        <ul class='mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2'>
          <li class='rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/5 p-5 text-left shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/10'>
            <p class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>登録不要ですぐ開始</p>
            <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200/80'>ゲストログインで利用が可能です。セットアップなしでテンポ良く練習できます。</p>
          </li>
          <li class='rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/5 p-5 text-left shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/10'>
            <p class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>牌効率を自動判定</p>
            <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200/80'>有効牌や向聴数の変化をリアルタイムに可視化します。</p>
          </li>
          <li class='rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/5 p-5 text-left shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/10'>
            <p class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>巻き戻し機能</p>
            <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200/80'>ミスした局面まで戻り、やり直すことが可能です。</p>
          </li>
          <li class='rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/5 p-5 text-left shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/10'>
            <p class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>ゲームモード</p>
            <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200/80'>トレーニングしたい能力に応じてモードを選択しましょう。</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <aside aria-labelledby='start-now-title' class='flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-cyan-500/15 bg-[#0a0d14]/80 p-4 text-center shadow-[0_24px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.55)] backdrop-blur'>
        <h2 id='start-now-title' class='mt-3 text-xl font-bold text-white'>今すぐ開始する</h2>
        <p id='login-options-description' class='mt-3 text-sm text-slate-200/80'>
          ログイン方法を選択してゲームを始めましょう。
        </p>
        <div class='mt-6 space-y-4'>
          <%= button_to '登録せずに利用開始する', '/guest_login',
            method: :post, data: { turbo: false },
            aria: { label: '登録不要ですぐにTenpai Speederを始める' },
            class: 'mx-auto block w-fit max-w-full min-w-[16rem] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 via-sky-400 to-emerald-400 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:text-slate-900 hover:shadow-[0_0px_30px_rgba(56,189,248,0.35)] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-cyan-200 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[#0a0d14]' %>
          <%= button_to 'Googleでログインする', @login_path,
            method: :post, data: { turbo: false },
            aria: { label: 'GoogleアカウントでTenpai Speederにログインする', describedby: 'login-options-description' },
            class: 'mx-auto block w-fit max-w-full min-w-[16rem] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/10 hover:shadow-[0_0px_30px_rgba(56,189,248,0.25)] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-cyan-200 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[#0a0d14]' %>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
